] and Puja [ https://substack.com/redirect/65a29795-ba39-41ec-9782-e478f6b1=
7a1a?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] f=
or editing! Keep an eye on Dan=E2=80=99s twitter [ https://substack.com/red=
irect/a4f52b22-f926-4616-b868-c51dde496bf4?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7Gn=
A_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] for a Create launch announcement at 11=
am EST =F0=9F=91=80.
Thanks for hanging out with us in our optimistic little corner of the inter=
net in 2022. Have a wonderful holiday season and I=E2=80=99ll see you in th=
e new year. It=E2=80=99s going to be fun.=20
Thanks for reading,=20
Packy

